\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Complex schedule trigger\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs26 \cf0 on:\
  schedule:\
    - cron: '0 */6 * * *'  # 00:00, 06:00, 12:00, 18:00 UTC daily\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 The schedule-based trigger in crons is complicated since the firing of that trigger does not depend on the activity from the user end or the changes to the coding. With the input condition being very verbose, the entire process becomes bifurcated into two different approaches.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

