\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Amazon S3 (static hosting) + CloudFront\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The build process in React creates HTML, CSS, and JS files statically, which can be served even without having to use a server. The files created can be stored inexpensively using S3 at a cost of $0.023 per gigabyte per month and distributed through CloudFront from more than 400 edge locations worldwide.\
